    1. Add a primary action button to complete the stage

    Between the inputs panel and the review table, add a primary action button area with the following behavior:

    Idle state — no unresolved Needs BU rows in the table:

        Primary button label: Save & Continue →
        Color: same primary green or blue used on other stage CTAs
